disruptions.description: Between northbound Bakerloo line trains terminating at Queen's Park and through Bakerloo line trains towards Stonebridge Park or Harrow & Wealdstone, or northbound London Overground trains. Step-free interchange will also be available between southbound Bakerloo line and London Overground services. Please ask staff in the ticket hall at the start of your journey to ensure the ramp will be available when you arrive at your destination.
